  "name": "Dark-Chocolate Ganache",
  "description": "Chocolate drizzle for the top — unsweetened baking chocolate melted with granulated Splenda and thinned with warm almond milk. Real cocoa-butter mouthfeel that cocoa powder can't fake; kept to a thin drizzle so the fat stays small (~98 cal for the whole cake). Sub-recipe (1 batch).",
