        "instructionText": "Melt the baking chocolate gently (microwave in 15-sec bursts, or a double boiler). Whisk in the Splenda and the WARM almond milk a little at a time until glossy and pourable — adding it cold can seize the chocolate. Use it warm; it sets as it cools."
